org.cef.handler

类 CefResourceHandlerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.callback.CefNativeAdapter
      • org.cef.handler.CefResourceHandlerAdapter
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    CefNative, CefResourceHandler 

    public abstract class CefResourceHandlerAdapter
extends CefNativeAdapter
implements CefResourceHandler
    An abstract adapter class for receiving resource requests. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating handler objects.
    用于接收资源请求的抽象适配器类。此类中的方法为空。此类存在是为了创建处理程序对象的便利。

      • canGetCookie

        public boolean canGetCookie(CefCookie cookie)
        从接口复制的说明: CefResourceHandler
        Return true if the specified cookie can be sent with the request or false otherwise. If false is returned for any cookie then no cookies will be sent with the request.
        如果指定的cookie可以随请求一起发送，则返回true，否则返回false。如果任何cookie返回false，则不会随请求一起发送cookie。

      • getResponseHeaders

        public void getResponseHeaders(CefResponse response,
                               IntRef response_length,
                               StringRef redirectUrl)
        从接口复制的说明: CefResourceHandler
        Retrieve response header information. If the response length is not known set |response_length| to -1 and ReadResponse() will be called until it returns false. If the response length is known set |response_length| to a positive value and ReadResponse() will be called until it returns false or the specified number of bytes have been read. Use the |response| object to set the mime type, http status code and other optional header values. To redirect the request to a new URL set |redirectUrl| to the new URL.
        检索响应头信息。如果响应长度未知set | response_length | to -1和ReadResponse（）将被调用，直到它返回false。如果响应长度已知set | response_length |到正值并且将调用ReadResponse（），直到它返回false或读取了指定的字节数。使用| response |对象设置mime类型，http状态代码和其他可选标头值。要将请求重定向到新的URL集| redirectUrl |到新的URL。
        指定者:
        getResponseHeaders 在接口中  CefResourceHandler

      • processRequest

        public boolean processRequest(CefRequest request,
                              CefCallback callback)
        从接口复制的说明: CefResourceHandler
        Begin processing the request. To handle the request return true and call CefCallback::Continue() once the response header information is available (CefCallback::Continue() can also be called from inside this method if header information is available immediately). To cancel the request return false.
        开始处理请求。处理请求返回true并在响应头信息可用时调用CefCallback :: Continue（）（如果头信息立即可用，也可以从此方法内部调用CefCallback :: Continue（））。要取消请求，请返回false。
        指定者:
        processRequest 在接口中  CefResourceHandler

      • readResponse

        public boolean readResponse(byte[] data_out,
                            int bytes_to_read,
                            IntRef bytes_read,
                            CefCallback callback)
        从接口复制的说明: CefResourceHandler
        Read response data. If data is available immediately copy up to |bytes_to_read| bytes into |data_out|, set |bytes_read| to the number of bytes copied, and return true. To read the data at a later time set |bytes_read| to 0, return true and call CefCallback::Continue() when the data is available. To indicate response completion return false.
        读取响应数据。如果数据可用，请立即复制到| bytes_to_read | bytes到| data_out |，set | bytes_read |到复制的字节数，并返回true。要在以后读取数据| bytes_read |为0，返回true并在数据可用时调用CefCallback :: Continue（）。表示响应完成返回false。
        指定者:
        readResponse 在接口中  CefResourceHandler
